[
  {
    "text": "Drive, boy! Drive!",
    "start": 0.633,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Mayday, mayday!",
    "start": 10.109,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "You're off course!",
    "start": 12.211,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 27.66,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 29.929,
    "duration": 2.203
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 32.932,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh...",
    "start": 34.667,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "I feel so serene\nnow that I'm away",
    "start": 35.701,
    "duration": 3.004
  },
  {
    "text": "from that homicidal maniac\nSpongeBob.",
    "start": 38.838,
    "duration": 3.37
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasping]",
    "start": 44.176,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "The brake, son!",
    "start": 53.419,
    "duration": 1.701
  },
  {
    "text": "Aye, aye, Sir!",
    "start": 55.254,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "Here you go, Sir.",
    "start": 57.757,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "All I had to do was unscrew\ntwo little bolts.",
    "start": 58.991,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna stop this thing.",
    "start": 61.594,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell my wife I love her!",
    "start": 63.796,
    "duration": 2.403
  },
  {
    "text": "Come get some!",
    "start": 69.936,
    "duration": 2.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Man down! Man down!",
    "start": 74.841,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, excuse me. Sorry!",
    "start": 77.877,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, SpongeBob!",
    "start": 79.245,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry, Patrick,\nI can't stop to talk right now.",
    "start": 80.779,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't see! I can't see!",
    "start": 84.784,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "My pants!",
    "start": 87.653,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey! I can't see!",
    "start": 89.055,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 96.028,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 100.366,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 103.836,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "Did I pass?",
    "start": 109.308,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, if there was",
    "start": 110.409,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "a \"destroy the city\"\npart of the test,",
    "start": 111.711,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "you would have.",
    "start": 114.046,
    "duration": 1.269
  },
  {
    "text": "The nerve of some people.",
    "start": 116.849,
    "duration": 1.636
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, look, Mr. Krabs!\nI'm actually driving!",
    "start": 126.726,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Good job, boy!",
    "start": 128.895,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "Phew.",
    "start": 141.04,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 151.183,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 154.987,
    "duration": 2.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, at least I didn't hit\nthe Krusty Krab that time.",
    "start": 160.226,
    "duration": 2.802
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing nervously]",
    "start": 163.162,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, this driver\nwith no regard for safety.",
    "start": 173.439,
    "duration": 3.137
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 176.709,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 180.145,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, at least he had\nhis seat belt on.",
    "start": 181.947,
    "duration": 3.004
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 185.884,
    "duration": 2.537
  },
  {
    "text": "Adjusting your mirrors.",
    "start": 192.158,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "What's our boat smarts\nboater up to now?",
    "start": 194.393,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "You guessed it.",
    "start": 197.296,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "He's adjusting his mirror\nbefore he begins boating,",
    "start": 198.765,
    "duration": 4.17
  },
  {
    "text": "unlike this degenerate boater.",
    "start": 203.069,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 204.803,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah, perfect.",
    "start": 206.038,
    "duration": 2.27
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, use your mirrors, fool!",
    "start": 209.174,
    "duration": 1.703
  },
  {
    "text": "Mirrors? Oh, that reminds me.\nI haven't adjusted this one yet.",
    "start": 211.01,
    "duration": 3.604
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah! Can't see!",
    "start": 215.515,
    "duration": 2.235
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 218.751,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 221.454,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 222.755,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Ow.",
    "start": 229.996,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, and most importantly,\na driver with boat smarts",
    "start": 231.597,
    "duration": 3.237
  },
  {
    "text": "always pays attention\nto his surroundings",
    "start": 234.967,
    "duration": 3.103
  },
  {
    "text": "and avoids distractions.",
    "start": 238.204,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "Notice how this driver's eyes\nare locked firmly on the road.",
    "start": 240.373,
    "duration": 4.871
  },
  {
    "text": "And here we have\nthe epitome of a driver",
    "start": 245.711,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "who is carelessly\ndistracting himself",
    "start": 248.481,
    "duration": 2.703
  },
  {
    "text": "from the road and safety.",
    "start": 251.317,
    "duration": 2.603
  },
  {
    "text": "[honking]",
    "start": 262.961,
    "duration": 1.803
  },
  {
    "text": "[honking]",
    "start": 269.268,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah! Jerk!",
    "start": 272.404,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi there!",
    "start": 274.139,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Help! Lunatic driver!",
    "start": 276.308,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "- [screaming]\n- How's it going?",
    "start": 278.244,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 280.345,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "- I can't feel my hair.\n- My leg!",
    "start": 281.58,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "SpongeBob, I mean,\na boater without boat smarts",
    "start": 284.216,
    "duration": 4.005
  },
  {
    "text": "shows contempt for his boater\nbrethren and the law.",
    "start": 288.354,
    "duration": 4.104
  },
  {
    "text": "La-la-la-la!",
    "start": 292.591,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Wee!",
    "start": 294.76,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi, Squidward. Hi, Mrs. Puff.",
    "start": 298.264,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 300.199,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 302.134,
    "duration": 2.837
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 305.971,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Looks like you guys\nforgot your boat smarts!",
    "start": 311.877,
    "duration": 3.171
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 315.181,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "Never mind.",
    "start": 321.086,
    "duration": 1.636
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm ready!\nI can do this, Mrs. Puff!",
    "start": 325.958,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "I can do it! I can do it!",
    "start": 327.493,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "The driving test is over,\nSpongeBob.",
    "start": 329.562,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Stop the boat!",
    "start": 331.564,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait! I can do this, Mrs. Puff!\nI can do this!",
    "start": 333.065,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "[Mrs. Puff]\nOh!",
    "start": 335.168,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "The road, SpongeBob!\nGet back on the road!",
    "start": 336.602,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "Gotta pass the test!\nGotta pass!",
    "start": 339.372,
    "duration": 1.634
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 341.139,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, what do you got\nagainst the melons?",
    "start": 342.908,
    "duration": 2.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Look out!",
    "start": 345.911,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "This must be the night driving\npart of the test.",
    "start": 347.179,
    "duration": 1.636
  },
  {
    "text": "[sirens]",
    "start": 349.782,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, look at all those police!",
    "start": 350.683,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "I wonder\nif the president's in town.",
    "start": 352.085,
    "duration": 1.834
  },
  {
    "text": "Look out!",
    "start": 354.052,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 355.387,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming continues]",
    "start": 359.825,
    "duration": 2.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Where did I go wrong?!",
    "start": 363.529,
    "duration": 2.236
  }
]